name: SuperLite 3 in 1 Series: Arcade Classic Syuu
overview: Superlite 3 in 1 - Arcade Classic Syuu is a compilation of 3 arcade games released for the Playstation One console: - Superlite 1500 Series - Qix 2000 - Space Chaser 2000 [Superlite 1500 Series] - Crazy Balloon 2000 [Superlite 1500 Series]
